    "ca203": {
        "vi": "Lấy một nửa số M-Win \"Đầu tư\" để chuyển vào \"Két bạc\". Chỉ được sử dụng tính năng 50:50 một lần sau mỗi lượt thắng",
        "en": "Take half of the \"Investment\" M-Win to move into \"Safe\". Only use 50:50 once per turn",
        "id": "Ambil setengah dari \"Investasi\" M-Win untuk pindah ke \"Aman\". Gunakan hanya 50:50 sekali per giliran",
        "th": "ใช้เวลาครึ่งหนึ่งของเกม \"การลงทุน\" เพื่อเข้าสู่ \"ปลอดภัย\" ใช้ 50:50 ครั้งต่อเทิร์นเท่านั้น",
