    "ca217": {
        "vi": "Luật chơi",
        "en": "The side has result nearly 9 score will win \\nAfter choosing the bet amount, you can bet on the gates: <color=#F4236DFF>The Banker Win (Banker)</color> / <color=#1686E4FF>The Player Win (Player)</color> / <color=#FF8400FF>Has one pair (Pair) </color>/<color=green>Draw (Tie)</color>.",
        "id": "Pihaknya memiliki hasil hampir 9 skor akan menang \\n Setelah memilih jumlah taruhan, Anda dapat bertaruh di gerbang: <color = # F4236DFF> Kemenangan Bankir (Bankir) </ color> / <color = # 1686E4FF> Pemain Menang (Pemain) </ color> / <color = # FF8400FF> Memiliki satu pasangan (Pasangan) </ color> / <color = hijau> Draw (Tie) </ color>.",
