        "en": "The side has the closest result to 9 points to win \\nYou can bet on the <color=#F4236DFF>Banker win (Banker)</color> / <color=#1686E4FF>Player win (Player)</color> / <color=#FF8400FF>Pair</color>/<color=green>Tie</color>.",
