        "en": "Minigame Crazy Bonus includes 24 cells corresponding to:\\n- 5 cell contain the letter C \\n- 4 cell contain the letter R\\n- 3 cell contain the letter A\\n- 2 cell contain the letter Z\\n- 1 cell contain the letter Y\\n- 4 cell contain the letter X1\\n- 3 cell contain the letter X2\\n- 2 cell contain the letter X3",
