    "dc19": {
        "vi": "Các chữ cái C R A Z Y xuất hiện ngẫu nhiên qua các lần quay.\\n\\nChọn hộp quà để tìm chữ cái và hệ số nhân. Mỗi lượt chơi có 10 lượt mở hộp quà.\\n\\n<color=cyan>Giải thưởng</color> = <color=cyan>tổng giá trị</color> (giá trị các ô chữ cái mở được) x <color=cyan>tổng hệ số nhân</color> (ban đầu là 1)\\n\\n<color=red>Giải đặc biệt</color> (mở đủ chữ CRAZY) = <color=red>tổng giá trị</color> x <color=red>tổng hệ số nhân</color> x <color=red>10</color>",
        "en": "The letters C R A Z Y appear randomly through the turns.\\n\\nSelect the gift box to find letters and multiplier. Each turn has 10 open gift boxes.\\n\\n<color=cyan>Awards</color> = <color=cyan>total of value</color> (The value of the letters is opened) x <color=cyan>total multiplier</color> (start with 1)\\n\\n<color=red>Special awards</color> (open enough CRAZY) = <color=red>total value</color> x <color=red>total multiplier</color> x <color=red>10</color>",
        "id": "Huruf C R A Z Y muncul secara acak melalui belokan. \\n\\n Pilih kotak hadiah untuk menemukan huruf dan pengganda. Setiap belokan memiliki 10 kotak hadiah terbuka. \\n\\n <color = cyan> Penghargaan </ color> = <color = cyan> total nilai </ color > (Nilai huruf dibuka) x <color = cyan> pengganda total </ color> (mulai dengan 1) \\n\\n <color = red> Penghargaan khusus </ color> (cukup terbuka GILA) = <color = red> nilai total </ color> x <color = red> total pengganda </ color> x <color = red> 10 </ color>",
        "km": "អក្សរ C R A Z ដែលលេចឡើងដោយចៃដន្យតាមរយៈការបង្វិល។ \\n\\n  ជ្រើសរើសប្រអប់កាដូ ដើម្បីស្វែងរកអក្សរ និងមេគុណ។ វេនលេងនីមួយៗ មាន10 ដងដើម្បីបើកប្រអប់កាដូ។ \\n\\n<color=cyan> រង្វាន់ </color> = <color=cyan> តម្លៃសរុប </color> (តម្លៃប្រអប់អក្សរបានរកឃើញ) x <color=cyan> មេគុណសរុប </color> (ដំបូងគស្មើ 1)\\n\\n<color=red> រង្វាន់ពិសេស </color> (រកបានអក្សរ CRAZY) = <color=red>  តម្លៃសរុប</color> x <color=red> មេគុណសរុប</color> x <color=red>10</color>",
        "th": "ตัวอักษร c y a ปรากฏขึ้นแบบสุ่มผ่านทางเลี้ยว \\n\\n เลือกกล่องของขวัญเพื่อค้นหาตัวอักษรและตัวคูณ แต่ละเทิร์นมีกล่องของขวัญแบบเปิด 10 ใบ \\n\\n <color = cyan> awards </ color> = <color = cyan> มูลค่ารวม </ color > (มูลค่าของตัวอักษรถูกเปิด) x <color = cyan> ตัวคูณทั้งหมด </ color> (เริ่มต้นด้วย 1) \\n\\n <color = red> รางวัลพิเศษ </ color> (เปิดมากพอที่บ้า) = <color = red> มูลค่ารวม </ color> x <color = แดง> ตัวคูณทั้งหมด </ color> x <color = red> 10 </ color>",
        "zh": "各字母C R A Z Y 通过各转次偶然出现.\\n\\n选择礼品盒来查找字母和乘系数。每回会有10次开的礼品盒.\\n\\n<color=cyan>奖励</color> = <color=cyan>总价值</color> (能打开各字母盒子的价值) x <color=cyan>总乘系数</color> (开始为1)\\n\\n<color=red>特别奖</color> (打开全部 CRAZY) = <color=red>总价值</color> x <color=red>总乘系数</color> x <color=red>10</color>"
    },
