        "en": "Event: <color=yellow>Play PhucSinh, X2 Jackpot</color> of minigame PhucSinh\\n\\nAt 12:30 pm on Tuesdays and Saturdays, to gratitude players, minigame PhucSinh there will be 22 jackpots in room 100 and 2 jackpots int room 100 is <color=yellow> X2(doubled) value </color>.\\n\\n For example:\\nAt the time of eating jar X2, the value of the jackpot is 6,000,000 and the payline payline is 100,000, the prize the player will receive is: 6,000,000 x 2 + 100,000 = 12,100,000\\n\\nNote:\\n- Room 100: The next X2 jackpot will be 3 times normal for the previous X2(ex: 1, 5, 9...).\\n- Room 1.000: Third and Seventh jackpot will be X2 from the gold time.\\n- Gold time start at 12:30 and end when rewarded 22 jackpots in room 100 and 2 jackpots in room 1.000;",
        "zh": "Event: <color=yellow>Play PhucSinh, X2 Jackpot</color> of minigame PhucSinh\\n\\n12:30 pm on Tuesdays and Saturdays, to gratitude players, minigame PhucSinh there will be 22 jackpots in room 100 and 2 jackpots int room 100 is <color=yellow> X2(doubled) value </color>.\\n\\n<color=yellow>Note:</color>\\n- Room 100: The next X2 jackpot will be 3 times normal for the previous X2(ex: 1, 5, 7...).\\n- Room 1.000: Tuesdays and Saturdays will be X2 from the gold time.\\n- Gold time start at 12:30 and end when rewarded 22 jackpots in room 100 and 2 jackpots in room 1.000;",
