        "en": "- For games that do not match (refund 100% of the bet amount), the system will not recognize and disregard the result of that game..\\n\\n- If in the winning streak, the player simultaneously meets the condition to be awarded 2 gift boxes, the system will give the player the gift box with the smallest value and end the winning streak to start recording a new winning sequence..\\n\\nFor example: if player wins game 1M, wins 2nd game 3M, wins third game 5M, the player is both eligible to receive Gold and Platinum gift boxes, but the system will reward player with a Golden gift box and finish accelerate this winning streak to begin recording a new winning streak..\\n\\nPlayers who have 4 slots to store gifts, in case there are 4 slots with 4 gift boxes (or gifts), they will not be able to receive additional gift boxes even if another winning chain has been met..\\n\\nEach gift box is valid for 24 hours from the time of receiving the gift box. If the player does not open it within 24 hours of receiving it, the gift box will disappear.\\n\\nAfter opening the gift box, players will randomly receive one of many valuable gifts and the corresponding time to wait for the reward.",
