        "en": "<color=yellow>Event: “Hunting for beautiful cards, winning Iphone\" of minigame High Low</color>\\n\\nTime: Event takes place every month, from the 1st to the last day of the month.\\n\\nContent:\\n- - Applies to all M-Win copper High Low minigames on M365.win portal\\n\\nRules:\\n- During the event period, customers participating in the M-Win High Low minigame have the opportunity to receive many valuable M-Win prizes for day prizes and 01 Iphone 15 Pro Max for the final prize .\\n- During a High Low minigame session, the system will automatically select 5 cards from the cards opened to be combined into the highest deck according to the rules of the Poker game (no card nature).\\n- Valid session is a session with at least 5 innings of play and the last round of play is a winner.\\n- Prize day statistics from 0h00 to 23h59.\\n\\nRanking criteria:\\n- The highest deck of cards the system records each day\\n- Biggest winnings\\n- The time to reach the highest card earlier (at the end of the session)",
