    "iap13": {
        "vi": "Tỉ lệ đổi <color=yellow>M-Win</color> sang XU: <color=yellow>1.000 M-Win = 100.000 XU</color>\\nGiới thiệu đồng Xu:\\n* Xu là đồng tiền chơi bàn thường trong game \\n* Xu sử dụng để tham gia sự kiện, mua các item Xu trong cửa hàng\\n* Xu không có tác dụng quy đổi sang <color=yellow>M-Win</color>\\n* Kiếm Xu bằng cách đăng nhập hàng ngày, đổi <color=yellow>M-Win</color> sang xu",
        "en": "Exchange rate from <color=yellow>M-Win</color> to XU: <color=yellow>1.000 M-Win = 100.000 XU</color>\\nXu coin introduction\\n* XU is a virtual currency to play in normal  tables.\\n* Xu are use to play in Events and buy XU items in shop.\\n* XU is not available to exchange to <color=yellow>M-Win</color>\\n* Earn free XU by login daily or exchange from <color=yellow>M-Win</color>.",
        "id": "Nilai tukar dari <color = yellow>> M-Win </ color> ke XU: <color = yellow> 1.000 M-Win = 100.000 XU </ color> \\n Xu coin Introduction \\n * XU adalah mata uang virtual untuk bermain dalam tabel normal. \\n * Xu digunakan untuk bermain di Acara dan membeli item XU di toko. \\n * XU tidak tersedia untuk ditukar dengan <color = yellow> M-Win </ color> \\n * Dapatkan XU gratis dengan masuk setiap hari atau tukar dari <color = yellow> M-Win </ color>.",
        "km": "អត្រានៃការប្តូរ <color=yellow>M-Win</color> ទៅ XU: <color=yellow>1.000 M-Win = 100.000 XU</color>\\n ឧទ្ទេសនាម coin \\n* Xu គឺជារូបិយប័ណ្ណល្បែងតុធម្មតាធម្មតានៅក្នុងហ្គេម \\n* Xu ត្រូវបានប្រើដើម្បីចូលរួមព្រឹត្តិការណ៍ ទិញបណ្តា item coin នៅក្នុងហាង \\n* Xu មិនមានប្រសិទ្ធិភាពប្តូរទៅជា<color=yellow>M-Win</color>\\n* រក Xu ដោយរបៀបចុះឈ្មោះរៀងរាល់ថ្ងៃ ប្តូរ <color=yellow>M-Win</color> ទៅ Xu។",
        "th": "อัตราแลกเปลี่ยนจาก <color = yellow> M-Win </ color> ถึง XU: <color = yellow> 1.000 M-Win = 100.000 XU </ color> \\n Xu coin Introduction \\n * XU เป็นสกุลเงินเสมือนในการเล่นในตารางปกติ \\n * Xu ใช้เล่นในกิจกรรมและซื้อสินค้า XU ในร้านค้า \\n * XU ไม่ได้เป็น สามารถแลกเปลี่ยนเป็น <color = yellow> M-Win </ color> \\n * รับ XU ฟรีโดยเข้าสู่ระบบทุกวันหรือแลกเปลี่ยนจาก <color = yellow> M-Win </ color>",
        "zh": "从<color=yellow>M-Win</color>到XU的汇率: <color=yellow>1.000 M-Win = 100.000 币</color>\\n 货币介绍:\\n* 币 是 游戏中普通盘的货币 \\n* 使用币参加事件, 购买商店中的item 币 \\n* 币不能兑换的作用 <color=yellow>M-Win</color>\\n* 赚币 的做法是每天登入 , 交换从<color=yellow>M-Win</color> 到 Xu"
    },
