        "en": "- Minimum transaction 300.000.\\n\\n- In case the wrong bank account information is entered, leading to the money being transferred to someone else's bank account, the publisher will not be responsible.\\n\\n<color=yellow>Note:</color> \\n-Double check your bank account information before Confirming your bank transfer request.",
