            "txt_reset_password_guide_sms": {
                "vi": "<i><color=#fffc00>Quy định:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Lấy lại mật khẩu bằng SMS:\nBước 1: Nhập tên tài khoản rồi ấn nút <color=#fffc00>Lấy mã OTP</c>\nđể nhận mã xác nhận\nBước 2: Nhập các thông tin theo yêu cầu và thực hiện\nđổi mật khẩu.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Lưu ý:</c>\nĐể thực hiện chức năng lấy mật khẩu bằng SMS, bạn\ncần phải kích hoạt bảo mật bằng SMS.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "en": "<i><color=#fffc00>Regulations:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Reset password via SMS:\nStep 1: Enter your account name and press <color=#fffc00>Get OTP</c>\nbutton to receive a verification code.\nStep 2: Enter the required information and change\nyour password.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Note:</c>\nTo use the SMS password recovery function, you\nmust activate SMS security.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "km": "<i><color=#fffc00>វិធានការ:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>ការប្រើប្រាស់លេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈ SMS:\nជំហានទី 1: បញ្ចូលឈ្មោះគណនីរបស់អ្នក ហើយចុចប៊ូតុង <color=#fffc00>យក OTP</c>\nដើម្បីទទួលលេខបញ្ជាក់។\nជំហានទី 2: បំពេញព័ត៌មានតាមការស្នើសុំ ហើយផ្លាស់ប្តូរលេខសម្ងាត់របស់អ្នក។\n\n<color=#fffc00>ចំណាំ:</c>\nដើម្បីប្រើមុខងារប្រើលេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈ SMS អ្នក\nត្រូវតែបើកសុវត្ថិភាព SMS។\n</color>\n</i>",
                "th": "<i><color=#fffc00>ข้อกำหนด:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>การกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่าน SMS:\nขั้นตอนที่ 1: ป้อนชื่อบัญชีของคุณแล้วกดปุ่ม <color=#fffc00>รับ OTP</c>\nเพื่อรับรหัสยืนยัน\nขั้นตอนที่ 2: ป้อนข้อมูลตามที่ร้องขอและดำเนินการเปลี่ยนรหัสผ่านของคุณ\n\n<color=#fffc00>หมายเหตุ:</c>\nในการใช้ฟังก์ชันกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่าน SMS คุณ\nต้องเปิดใช้งานความปลอดภัยผ่าน SMS\n</color>\n</i>",
                "id": "<i><color=#fffc00>Peraturan:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Memulihkan kata sandi melalui SMS:\nLangkah 1: Masukkan nama akun Anda lalu\ntekan tombol <color=#fffc00>Dapatkan OTP</c> untuk menerima\nkode verifikasi.\nLangkah 2: Masukkan informasi yang diminta\ndan ubah kata sandi Anda.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Catatan:</c>\nUntuk menggunakan fungsi pemulihan kata\nsandi melalui SMS, Anda harus mengaktifkan\nkeamanan SMS.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "zh": "<i><color=#fffc00>规定：</c>\n<color=#ffffff>通过短信找回密码：\n步骤 1：输入您的账户名称，然后点击 <color=#fffc00>获取 OTP</c>\n按钮以接收验证码。\n步骤 2：输入所需信息并更改密码。\n\n<color=#fffc00>注意：</c>\n要使用短信找回密码功能，您\n必须启用短信安全验证。\n</color>\n</i>"
            },
            "txt_reset_password_guide_email": {
                "vi": "<i><color=#fffc00>Quy định:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Lấy lại mật khẩu bằng email:\nBước 1: Nhập đầy đủ thông tin rồi nhấn tiếp tục để\nnhận mã bảo mật bằng email\nBước 2: Nhập thông tin và thực hiện đổi mật khẩu\n\n<color=#fffc00>Lưu ý:</c>\nĐể thực hiện chức năng lấy mật khẩu bằng email, bạn\ncần phải kích hoạt bảo mật bằng Email.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "en": "<i><color=#fffc00>Regulations:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Reset password via email:\nStep 1: Enter all required information and press\ncontinue to receive a security code via email.\nStep 2: Enter the required information and change\nyour password.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Note:</c>\nTo use the email password recovery function, you\nmust activate Email security.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "km": "<i><color=#fffc00>វិធានការ:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>ការប្រើប្រាស់លេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈអ៊ីមែល:\nជំហានទី 1: បញ្ចូលព័ត៌មានទាំងអស់ ហើយចុចបន្តដើម្បី\nទទួលលេខសុវត្ថិភាពតាមរយៈអ៊ីមែល។\nជំហានទី 2: បំពេញព័ត៌មានតាមការស្នើសុំ ហើយផ្លាស់ប្តូរលេខសម្ងាត់។\n\n<color=#fffc00>ចំណាំ:</c>\nដើម្បីប្រើមុខងារប្រើលេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈអ៊ីមែល អ្នក\nត្រូវតែបើកសុវត្ថិភាពអ៊ីមែល។\n</color>\n</i>",
                "th": "<i><color=#fffc00>ข้อกำหนด:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>การกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่านอีเมล:\nขั้นตอนที่ 1: ป้อนข้อมูลทั้งหมดแล้วกดดำเนินการต่อเพื่อ\nรับรหัสความปลอดภัยทางอีเมล\nขั้นตอนที่ 2: ป้อนข้อมูลที่จำเป็นและเปลี่ยนรหัสผ่านของคุณ\n\n<color=#fffc00>หมายเหตุ:</c>\nในการใช้ฟังก์ชันกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่านอีเมล คุณ\nต้องเปิดใช้งานความปลอดภัยของอีเมล\n</color>\n</i>",
                "id": "<i><color=#fffc00>Peraturan:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Memulihkan kata sandi melalui email:\nLangkah 1: Masukkan semua informasi yang diperlukan\nlalu tekan lanjutkan untuk menerima kode\nkeamanan melalui email.\nLangkah 2: Masukkan informasi yang diminta\ndan ubah kata sandi Anda.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Catatan:</c>\nUntuk menggunakan fungsi pemulihan kata sandi\nmelalui email, Anda harus mengaktifkan keamanan email.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "zh": "<i><color=#fffc00>规定：</c>\n<color=#ffffff>通过电子邮件找回密码：\n步骤 1：输入所有必填信息，然后点击继续，以\n通过电子邮件接收安全代码。\n步骤 2：输入所需信息并更改密码。\n\n<color=#fffc00>注意：</c>\n要使用电子邮件找回密码功能，您\n必须启用电子邮件安全验证。\n</color>\n</i>"
            },
            "txt_reset_password_guide_telesafe": {
                "vi": "<i><color=#fffc00>Quy định:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Lấy lại mật khẩu bằng Telesafe:\nBước 1: Nhập tên tài khoản rồi ấn nút <color=#fffc00>Lấy mã OTP</c>\nđể nhận mã xác nhận.\nBước 2: Nhập các thông tin theo yêu cầu và thực hiện\nđổi mật khẩu.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Lưu ý:</c>\nĐể thực hiện chức năng lấy mật khẩu bằng TeleSafe,\nbạn cần phải kích hoạt bảo mật bằng TeleSafe.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "en": "<i><color=#fffc00>Regulations:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Reset password via Telesafe:\nStep 1: Enter your account name and press <color=#fffc00>Get OTP</c>\nto receive a verification code.\nStep 2: Enter the required information and change\nyour password.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Note:</c>\nTo use the TeleSafe password recovery function,\nyou must activate TeleSafe security.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "km": "<i><color=#fffc00>វិធានការ:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>ការប្រើប្រាស់លេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈ Telesafe:\nជំហានទី 1: បញ្ចូលឈ្មោះគណនីរបស់អ្នក ហើយចុចប៊ូតុង <color=#fffc00>យក OTP</c>\nដើម្បីទទួលលេខបញ្ជាក់។\nជំហានទី 2: បំពេញព័ត៌មានតាមការស្នើសុំ ហើយផ្លាស់ប្តូរលេខសម្ងាត់។\n\n<color=#fffc00>ចំណាំ:</c>\nដើម្បីប្រើមុខងារប្រើលេខសម្ងាត់តាមរយៈ TeleSafe អ្នក\nត្រូវតែបើកសុវត្ថិភាព TeleSafe។\n</color>\n</i>",
                "th": "<i><color=#fffc00>ข้อกำหนด:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>การกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่าน Telesafe:\nขั้นตอนที่ 1: ป้อนชื่อบัญชีของคุณแล้วกด <color=#fffc00>รับ OTP</c>\nเพื่อรับรหัสยืนยัน\nขั้นตอนที่ 2: ป้อนข้อมูลที่จำเป็นและเปลี่ยนรหัสผ่านของคุณ\n\n<color=#fffc00>หมายเหตุ:</c>\nในการใช้ฟังก์ชันกู้คืนรหัสผ่านผ่าน TeleSafe คุณ\nต้องเปิดใช้งานความปลอดภัยของ TeleSafe\n</color>\n</i>",
                "id": "<i><color=#fffc00>Peraturan:</c>\n<color=#ffffff>Memulihkan kata sandi melalui Telesafe:\nLangkah 1: Masukkan nama akun Anda lalu tekan\n<color=#fffc00>Dapatkan OTP</c>untuk menerima kode\nverifikasi.\nLangkah 2: Masukkan informasi yang diminta\ndan ubah kata sandi Anda.\n\n<color=#fffc00>Catatan:</c>\nUntuk menggunakan fungsi pemulihan kata\nsandi melalui TeleSafe, Anda harus mengaktifkan\nkeamanan TeleSafe.\n</color>\n</i>",
                "zh": "<i><color=#fffc00>规定：</c>\n<color=#ffffff>通过 TeleSafe 找回密码：\n步骤 1：输入您的账户名称，然后点击 <color=#fffc00>获取 OTP</c>\n按钮以接收验证码。\n步骤 2：输入所需信息并更改密码。\n\n<color=#fffc00>注意：</c>\n要使用 TeleSafe 找回密码功能，您\n必须启用 TeleSafe 安全验证。\n</color>\n</i>"
            },
